cc:Work.dc:title: Lady in an Onsen Remix (Stripped back)
cc:Work.dc:description: A remix of J4p4n's wonderful Lady In An Onsen. I've stripped it back and inverted the colour. I've tried to make it resemble an oriental ink painting. Hope you enjoy. Would make a lovely poster as well as the original.
